---
title: Glazed Bison Meatballs with Mini Loaded Baked Potatoes
description: Fun is on the menu tonight with two top party snacks on one dinner plate! Sweet-and-sticky glazed meatballs are served alongside mini loaded baked potatoes with all the fixins – bacon, cheddar, sour cream and green onions!
